sequenceDiagram
    actor M as Manager
    participant UI as YogaApp UI
    participant API as API Server
    participant DB as MongoDB

    M->>UI: Click "+ Add Package"
    UI->>M: Display package form

    M->>UI: Enter package name, category, number of classes, class type, start date, end date, price
    M->>UI: Submit

    UI->>API: POST /packages
    API->>DB: Count existing packages (for packageId generation)
    API->>DB: Save package with generated packageId (e.g. P00001)
    API-->>UI: 201 with package and confirmation message

    UI->>M: Display confirmation "Package has been added. Package ID: P00001."
